                        <condition key="deficient">The Ms. shows traces of extensive use. Several
                           fols. are stained with wax and dirt. Some words are illegible or barely
                           legible on several fols. (e.g., on <locus target="#11v">11v</locus>, 12r,
                           12v, 19v, 20r). <locus target="#30">30</locus> has been damaged by
                           rodents and was repaired. The original sewing and binding has been
                           destroyed and was repaired with different kinds of threads (synthetic,
                           textile, vegetal). f. 1 is made of two pieces of parchment sewn together
                           with a parchment strip. The last two fols. (29, 30) are almost detached
                           from the Ms. The back board is broken and was repaired with different
                           kinds of threads (synthetic, textile, vegetal).</condition>
